wiki.content: “Yours,” a heart-touching ballad, works as one of the leading songs for the Korean TV drama, Jirisan (지리산), and is introduced in Episode 6. The song marks the second release, after “죽어도 너야 (It’s Definitely You)” from the drama Hwarang (화랑), sung by Jin which works as the soundtrack for the tv series. Jirisan (지리산), directed by Lee Eung Bok (이응복), is one of the most anticipated Korean series of 2021. This mystery thriller follows the story of a dedicated team of rangers working at the Jiri Mountain National Park—the biggest and the oldest in South Korea. Read more on Last.fm.
